shapes3d.utils
Class RotOrder

java.lang.Object
  shapes3d.utils.RotOrder
All Implemented Interfaces:
VectorConstants
public final class RotOrder
extends Object
implements VectorConstants

This class is a utility representing a rotation order specification for Cardan or Euler angles specification. This class cannot be instantiated by the user. He can only use one of the twelve predefined supported orders as an argument to either the Rotation#Rotation(RotationOrder,double,double,double) constructor or the Rotation#getAngles method.

Since:
1.2
